Marc Yaffee https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Marc_Yaffee 0 Marc Yaffee (born January 15, 1961) is a Native American comedian, writer and actor. Marc began doing stand-up comedy in 1999 after attending a comedy workshop at Laughs Unlimited ComedyClub in Sacramento, CA. Since then he has performed in 41 states and 9 countries.
